H4^^Early forcing^^^^^^^Miriam was able to "look ahead" one move early in her play.  (Her fight with Robby derived from her fear -- well founded -- that he would try to block her corners strategy on his next move.)  There are two incident in the core period of The Intimate Study  where Miriam was,
